snippet.title: Forever World Cup Simulator can simulate forever while you sleep. #football #soccer
snippet.description:
Available in the next update! This simulator may eventually live up to its name. It can play with itself forever without using your hands! You can just hit the "Forever" button, sleep for hours, and wake up to find out what has happened over hundreds of years in the game world!

Simulator homepage: https://simcups.com

Discord server: https://discord.com/invite/gEFrpKDjum
